Package: grainchanger
Title: Calculate Functions Using Moving Window and Upscale
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Laura", "Graham", email = "LauraJaneEGraham@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package acts as a wrapper for the raster package and allows users to upscale fine resolution rasters to a coarser gird using specified functions either using moving windows or not. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
